text: Eunidia semirufa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1916. It is known from Tanzania and Kenya.BioLib.cz - Eunidia semirufa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1916
